1.3.0
- Upload Order is now the default sorting mode.
- Added sort mode cycling: Upload Order → A-Z → Z-A → Upload Order.
- Increased maximum playable file path length from 56 to 200 characters.
- Added automatic scrolling marquee for long song titles in the Now Playing display.
- Added delay before title scrolling marquee begins.
- Added continuous playlist playback starting from any selected song.
- Removed dedicated PLAY ALL menu option.
- Renamed SHUFFLE PLAY ALL to RANDOMIZE.
- Renamed BACK TO PLAYLISTS to BACK.
- Playlist changes no longer stop the currently playing song.
- Entering playlists while music is playing now preserves playback.
- Added TAB menu audio feedback when entering playlists during playback.
- Reduced delay when entering playlists.
- Updated cursor handling to use native Pip-Boy wheel acceleration values.
- Cursor movement now supports multi-row wheel events.
- Improved wheel navigation consistency.
- Prevented scroll sounds from playing when already at the top/bottom of a list.
- Reversed volume adjustment direction to match wheel movement.
- Waveform display now remains active while adjusting volume.
- Reduced Settings Menu long-press delay from 600ms to 250ms.
- Improved memory handling and runtime stability.
- Improved overall application responsiveness.
Modified and expanded by Joe Byers.

