https://github.com/CodyTolene/pip-boy-3000-holotapes/pull/27
- Create the "MUSIC" folder automatically on launch if it is missing so the app no longer fails to load.
- Show a "NO PLAYLISTS FOUND" message linking to pip-boy.com when no station playlists exist.

1.2.0
https://github.com/CodyTolene/pip-boy-3000-holotapes/pull/25
- On long press/hold of the left wheel button, open the settings menu. Close with another long hold.
- Sorting functionality button moved into the new settings menu.
- New setting added for controlling screen brightness from the settings menu.
- New setting for controlling audio volume from the settings menu.
- Read version dynamically from "APPINFO/IPIP.info" instead of hardcoding it in the app.
- Restore volume to system settings on exit.
- Restore brightness to system settings on exit.

